<%- include('../../../_partials/header'); -%>

    <div class="px-6 lg:px-16 py-6 w-full">
        <h2 class="text-gray-700 font-semibold text-3xl pt-6">About <span class="underline text-lyrics-600 font-bold">Lyrics</span></h2>
        <div class="w-3/3 md:w-2/3 text-gray-600">
            <p class="mb-2">Have you ever wanted to sing a song but you couldnâ€™t find the lyrics quickly ? With Sooneos Lyrics, simply launch any song on your Spotify account (free and premium) and get the lyrics automatically on <a href="<%= configuration.base_url %>lyrics" class="text-lyrics-700 hover:text-lyrics-500 underline">this page</a></p>
            <p class="mb-2">The algorithm searches the lyrics, thanks to the title and the artists of the songs, on the website <a href="https://genius.com" target="blank" class="text-lyrics-700 hover:text-lyrics-500 underline">Genius</a>. If no lyrics are found (this is possible for lesser known songs and not available on <a href="https://genius.com" target="blank" class="text-lyrics-700 hover:text-lyrics-500 underline">Genius</a>) you will get an error notification</p>
            <p class="mb-2">Sooneos Lyrics detect when you change music and the lyrics will update automatically.</p>
        </div>

